* IN BETWEEN THE LINES
THERE'S A LOT OF OBSCURITY *

42:21.300 --> 42:24.599
* I'M NOT INCLINED
TO RESIGN TO MATURITY *

42:24.650 --> 42:28.142
* IF IT'S ALL RIGHT
THEN YOU'RE ALL WRONG *

42:28.190 --> 42:31.978
* BUT WHY BOUNCE AROUND
TO THE SAME DAMN SONG? *

42:32.020 --> 42:36.992
* YOU'D RATHER RUN
WHEN YOU CAN CRAWL *

42:39.440 --> 42:42.841
* I KNOW YOU KNOW
THAT I'M NOT TELLING THE TRUTH *

42:42.880 --> 42:45.815
* I KNOW YOU KNOW
THEY JUST DON'T HAVE ANY PROOF *

42:45.850 --> 42:48.785
* EMBRACE THE DECEPTION
LEARN HOW TO BEND *

42:48.830 --> 42:50.491
* YOUR WORST INHIBITIONS

42:50.530 --> 42:53.067
